title: Godman (Frederic du Cane)
body: In his book entitled Natural History of the Azores (London, 1870), he published a list, organized by W. Mitten, of the Muscineas of Madeira, the Canaries, and the Azores, as well as a work by H. C. Watson on Azorean botany, which contains some observations that may be beneficial to those studying the flora of our archipelago.

W. Mitten: Organizer of the list of Muscineas

1870: Publication of the book Natural History of the Azores
